              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": ["production-cycle", "1", "close"]
            },
            "description": "Closes the cycle. Requires at least 1 harvest. Calculates revenue, costs, gross margin, real yield, and generates yield alert if below 20% of historical average."
